It’s been 15 days now…
In my previous reel, I shared how I suddenly got this infection and had to rush to the hospital because the symptoms were just too uncomfortable. The doctor recommended a 6-day medication and thankfully, I’m fully fine now. 🙏
But what truly surprised me was what happened after that video…
My DMs were flooded with messages. That’s when I realized so many girls out there are silently going through the same discomfort. 😞
So I decided to share what really helped me not just the medicine, but two simple home remedies my mom recommended.
They made a huge difference especially with the burning sensation while peeing, itching and discomfort.
If you’re someone who’s not dealing with a major infection but still experiencing mild issues like burning or itching this Ayurvedic remedy might help you too. 🌿
It’s safe, natural and has no side effects.

Please don’t ignore your body’s signals.
Take care and always listen to what it’s trying to tell you. 💛
